            <title>首款 PCIe 5.0 SSD 笔记本：联想 ThinkPad X1 Carbon Aura 2025 AI 元启版发布，15999 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/815/649.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/815/649.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
